OL,3,CThames Water delays challenging
OL,4,Cwatchdog's ruling on bills
OL,6,FThames Water has agreed to delay a
OL,7,Fpossible appeal over how much it can
OL,8,Fcharge for customer bills while talks
OL,9,Fover a refinancing deal with potential
OL,10,Fbuyers take place.
OL,12,FThe UK's biggest water firm said it
OL,13,Fhad agreed with Ofwat to defer the
OL,14,Fcase until further notice.
OL,16,FIt had previously asked the water
OL,17,Fwatchdog to refer its price review to
OL,18,Fthe UK's Competition and Markets
OL,19,FAuthority (CMA).
