OL,3,CThames Water delays challenging
OL,4,Cwatchdog's ruling on bills
OL,6,FIt is among a number of utilities
OL,7,Ffirms urging regulators to allow them
OL,8,Fto charge customers more for bills
OL,9,Fthan previously granted, having argued
OL,10,Fthat what was allowed by Ofwat was not
OL,11,Fenough to support investment and
OL,12,Fimprovement plans.
OL,14,FDoing so was "in the interests of our
OL,15,Fcustomers and the environment", Thames
OL,16,Fsaid in February.
OL,18,FDeferring the potential appeal comes
OL,19,Fafter a group of its investors offered
OL,20,Fa rescue deal for the troubled utility
OL,21,Ffirm.
