OL,3,CThames Water delays challenging
OL,4,Cwatchdog's ruling on bills
OL,6,FLondon & Valley Water submitted a
OL,7,Fturnaround proposal earlier this month
OL,8,Fwhich is currently being scrutinised
OL,9,Fwith regulators.
OL,11,FA spokesman for the consortium said:
OL,12,F"Today's announcement and the further
OL,13,Fextension agreed follows discussion
OL,14,Fwith Ofwat, EA (Environment Agency)
OL,15,Fand DWI (Drinking Water Inspectorate)
OL,16,Fand continued progress to develop a
OL,17,Fsustainable solution which will
OL,18,Fdeliver improvements for Thames
OL,19,FWater's customers, employees and the
OL,20,Fenvironment.
