OL,3,CThames Water delays challenging
OL,4,Cwatchdog's ruling on bills
OL,6,F"We will continue to work at pace with
OL,7,Fall stakeholders with a view to
OL,8,Fconcluding discussions and agreeing
OL,9,Fthe terms of a transaction as soon as
OL,10,Fpossible, achieving an outcome that is
OL,11,Ffirst and foremost in customers'
OL,12,Finterests and avoids the unnecessary
OL,13,Fcost, risk and delay of a special
OL,14,Fadministration."
OL,16,FA spokesman for Ofwat said: "Thames
OL,17,FWater has requested a further deferral
OL,18,Fof its 2024 Price Review final
OL,19,Fdetermination reference to the
OL,20,FCompetition and Markets Authority
OL,21,F(CMA).
