OL,3,CThames Water delays challenging
OL,4,Cwatchdog's ruling on bills
OL,6,F"Given the ongoing discussions with
OL,7,Fthe company's creditors, Ofwat has
OL,8,Fagreed to this request and informed
OL,9,Fthe CMA.
OL,11,F"Thames Water and Ofwat agree that at
OL,12,Fthis point in the review process there
OL,13,Fis no benefit in setting a definitive
OL,14,Fexpected end date for the deferral
OL,15,Fdecision."
